Package edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course

Class Activity

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course.Activity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Conflict
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Course
    public abstract class Activity
extends java.lang.Object
implements Conflict
    This superclass saves the title, meeting days, starting and ending times of any given course. It also contains code to determine if any two activities are equivalent.
    Author:
    Alex Bernard
